OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FThe father of schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,7,Fwho was murdered in a row over a teddy
OL,8,Fbear has said the conviction of her
OL,9,Fkiller is a "message" that violence
OL,10,Fagainst young women "will not go
OL,11,Funanswered".
OL,13,FElianne's father Michael Andam,
OL,14,Fspeaking outside the Old Bailey
OL,15,Ffollowing the conviction of Hassan
OL,16,FSentamu, 18, on Thursday, said: "The
OL,17,Fverdict today is the first step
OL,18,Ftowards justice for Elianne, but also
OL,19,Fa message that violence and knife
OL,20,Fcrime, especially towards young women,
OL,21,Fwill not go unanswered.
