OL,6,F"Today, we choose not to dwell on the
OL,7,Fpain of the trial, but instead to
OL,8,Fhonour Elianne's memory."
OL,10,FHe also said: "Her death has left a
OL,11,Fvoid in our lives that can never be
OL,12,Ffilled."
OL,14,FHassan Sentamu, 18, had a history of
OL,15,Fattacking girls and carrying knives
OL,16,Fbefore he stabbed the popular
OL,17,Fschoolgirl in the neck outside the
OL,18,FWhitgift centre in Croydon, south-east
OL,19,FLondon.
