OL,6,FAt Sentamu's trial, the prosecution
OL,7,Fclaimed the teenager had reacted to
OL,8,Fbeing splashed with water the day
OL,9,Fbefore and had lashed out at Elianne
OL,10,Fin a fit of "white hot" rage.
OL,12,FProsecutor Alex Chalk KC said: "He was
OL,13,Fangry on September 27, having brooded
OL,14,Fon the insult and he took the knife to
OL,15,Fthe scene to reassert dominance.
OL,17,F"He exacted vengeance on a young girl
OL,18,Fclearly running away from him and
OL,19,Fposing no threat."
