OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FAmid the public shock and outcry at
OL,7,Fthe killing, rap star Stormzy joined
OL,8,Fmembers of the community at a
OL,9,Fcandlelit vigil for Elianne in October
OL,10,F2023. Elianne aspired to become a
OL,11,Fhuman rights lawyer.
OL,13,FSentamu, who admitted manslaughter,
OL,14,Fclaimed his autism affected his
OL,15,Fability to exercise self control and
OL,16,Fwas therefore not guilty of murder.
OL,18,FHowever, the prosecution rejected the
OL,19,Fassertion saying neither his autism
OL,20,Fnor his troubled background provided
OL,21,Fan excuse for murder.
