OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FThe trial heard Sentamu had a long
OL,7,Fhistory of volatile and violent
OL,8,Fbehaviour, having been cautioned for
OL,9,Ftaking a knife to school, and, while
OL,10,Fawaiting trial for Elianne's murder,
OL,11,Fthreatened to "do it again".
OL,13,FFollowing a three-week Old Bailey
OL,14,Ftrial a jury found Sentamu, from New
OL,15,FAddington, near Croydon, guilty of
OL,16,Fmurder by a majority of 10 to two and
OL,17,Funanimously guilty of possession of a
OL,18,Fblade.
