OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FThere were shouts of "yes" and
OL,7,F"murderer" from the public gallery as
OL,8,Fthe jury delivered the verdicts after
OL,9,Fdeliberating for 11 hours and 42
OL,10,Fminutes.
OL,12,FSentamu leaned against the front of
OL,13,Fthe dock crying and wiping his eyes as
OL,14,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb thanked and
OL,15,Fdischarged the jurors.
OL,17,FAdjourning sentencing until March 13
OL,18,Ffor reports, the senior judge told the
OL,19,Fteenager: "I understand you must be
OL,20,Fvery shocked and take time to get used
OL,21,Fto what has happened."
