OL,6,FThree dock officers supported Sentamu
OL,7,Fas he was led down to the cells.
OL,9,FPaying tribute to Elianne, the
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police officer, who led
OL,11,Fthe murder investigation, said: "What
OL,12,Fhas really stuck with me is that
OL,13,FElianne always did what she thought
OL,14,Fwas right and stood up for her friend.
OL,16,F"We heard from her family during the
OL,17,Fcourse of this investigation that
OL,18,FElianne wanted to be a human rights
OL,19,Flawyer.
